snippet.title: Paperbark - Pre-Order from the App Store
snippet.description:
Paperbark is now available for Pre-Order from the App Store!
https://itunes.apple.com/au/app/paperbark/id1155399928?mt=8

Follow a sleepy wombat who spends its day exploring and foraging, while in search for a new home. 

Wander through a beautifully stylised interpretation of Australia, and watch as you bring the illustrated landscape to life, through vibrant watercolours and sounds.

Story by: Renee Treml
Music by: Biddy Conner

www.paperbarkgame.com
www.twitter.com/paperbarkgame
